Package org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.ui.commons.controller.base

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InstantiableController
    Represents a controller that is able to create a Node for a given FXML asset and bound itself to that node.
    InstantiableControllerView
    Represents a controller that is able to create a Node for an already known FXML asset.
    InstantiableReinitializableControllerView
    Represents an InstantiableControllerView that can be reinitialized for make the view consistent with the model.
    Reinitializable
    Represents an entity that can be reinitialized.
    RootController
    Represents a controller that is able to provide the stage of the StageAware interface by retrieving it from the root element of the view (which must be provided by the entities that inherit from this one).
    StageAware
    Represents an entity that is aware and thus provide a Stage.
